      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">[South Australia. ¶ (A) ¶ APPLICATION TO BRING LANDS UNDER THE PROVISIONS OF THE REAL PROPERTY ACT OF 1861. ¶ I,  ¶ Louis Almers ¶  of Adelaide in the Province of South Australia, butcher  ¶ do declar...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">63.07.07</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">Transfer of Title</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="background-color: #ffff00; ">archival locaton?,</seg> SA.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">[South Australia.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">(A)</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">APPLICATION TO BRING LANDS UNDER THE PROVISIONS OF THE REAL PROPERTY ACT OF 1861.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I, <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Louis Almers</hi>
               </seg> of Adelaide in the Province of South Australia, butcher <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">do declare that</seg> I am <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">seised of an estate of freehold</seg> in fee simple <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">in all</seg> that piece <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">of land situated in</seg> the the Village of <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Tanunda</hi>
               </seg>, being the allotment numbered “<seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">11</hi>
               </seg>” containing one acre or thereabouts, bounded as appears by plan in the margin hereof and therein coloured red<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">63-07-07_image01.jpg</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">which </seg>piece <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">of land is of the value of</seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Sixteen Pounds Sterling</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">and no more, and is </seg>part of the Country Section of land <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">originally granted to</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Several spaces in the sentence that follows have not been filled in.</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="12"/>by land grant, under the hand and seal of</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="20"/>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">of the Province of South Australia, dated the <space unit="chars" quantity="6"/>day of <space unit="chars" quantity="11"/>, <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>numbered</seg> 39 <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">in the plan of the said</seg> Hundred <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">of</seg> Moorooroo <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">as delineated on the public maps of the Province deposited in the Survey Office in Adelaide: And I do further declare that I am not aware of any mortgage, encumbrance, or claim affecting the said lands, or that any person hath any claim, estate, or interest in the said lands at law or in equity, in possession or in expectancy, other than is set forth and stated as follows, that is to say—</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">That I have sold the said piece of land to Ferdinand Jacob Heinrich Müller of Melbourne in the Province of Victoria Esqre M.D. Ph.D.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">And I further declare there is no person in possession or occupation of the said lands adversely to my estate or interest therein, and that the said land is now </seg>in the occupation of Carl von Bertouch <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">and that </seg>Thomas Smith and – Lutze and other trustees are owners of contiguous land <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">and that there are no deeds or instruments of title affecting such land in my possession or under my control, other than those enumerated in the Schedule hereto: And I made this solemn declaration, conscientiously believing the same to be true.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dated at</seg> Adelaide<seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; "> this </seg>seventh<seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; "> day of </seg>July<seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; "> 186</seg>3.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Louis Almers</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">Made and subscribed by the above-named</seg> Louis Almers<seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; "> on this </seg>seventh<seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; "> day of </seg>July <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">in the presence of me</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">F. Krichauff J. P.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">I,</seg> Louis Almers<seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; "> the above declarant, do hereby apply to have the piece of land described in the above declaration brought under the provisions of the Real Property Act of 1861.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dated at </seg>Adelaide<seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; "> this </seg>seventh<seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; "> day of </seg>July<seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; "> 186</seg>3.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Louis Almers</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">Witness to signature–</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">F. E. Krichauff J. P.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">To the Registrar-General</seg>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">–</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I, the above-named declarant, hereby request you to issue the Certificate of Title for the above mentioned </seg>piece<seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; "> of land, in the name of</seg> Ferdinand Jacob Heinrich Müller Doctor of Philosophy and of Medicine, Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Louis Almers<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Marginal annotations: 'Certificate issued Vol: XLV Folio 194 13/11/63' and 'I consent hereto John B. [Speng] official [...]'. 'Witness to signature F. Krichauff J. P.'</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See also Transfer of Title, 15 December 1865 (in this edition as 65-12-15b).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">Witness to signature</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">F. E. Krichauff J. P.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">[This application is correct for the purposes of the Real Property Act.]</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">F. E. Krichauff</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Lic. Broker</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">SCHEDULE REFERRED TO.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Conveyance Charles Flaxman to Louis Almers dated June 22nd 1848.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
